by bgotink at 2014-09-26T22:55:24Z

I love the idea, but what if you have this one piece of code where you don't want strict matching?

The same goes for some other fixers as well actually. Perhaps it would be nice to have some sort of php-cs-fixer directives users can add in the code? For example:
```php
// @pcf off strict_param
$result = in_array($needle, $haystack);
// @pcf on strict_param
```

