by keradus at 2014-09-28T21:00:19Z

All fixers at contrib level need to be manually enabled. If one don't want to use that rule - just do not enable this fixer.

I am against comment-directives to ignore some code in rules:
* fixer is a rule. one should either follow it of not. no exception
* exception will produce total mess in fixer code
